data.text:
Chris Kaman - Points

Chris Kaman scores a career high 29 points (2009)

On December 22, 2009, Chris Kaman set his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 29 points in LA Clippers's road loss against Houston, 108-99. He also had 7 rebounds, 3 assists and 2 blocks. He shot 13/21 from two, shooting at 61.9% from the field. He also shot 3/5 from the free-throw line.

Chris Kaman - Rebounds

Chris Kaman grabs a career high 23 rebounds (2006)

On March 13, 2006, Chris Kaman set his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 23 rebounds in LA Clippers's home win against Minnesota, 95-87. He also had 24 points, 1 assist, 4 steals and 3 blocks.

Chris Kaman - Assists

Chris Kaman gives a career high 8 assists (2012)

On March 07, 2012, Chris Kaman set his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 8 assists in New Orleans's road loss against Sacramento, 99-98. He also had 18 points, 11 rebounds and 2 blocks.

Chris Kaman - Steals

Chris Kaman has a career high 4 steals (2006)

On March 13, 2006, Chris Kaman set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 4 steals in LA Clippers's home win against Minnesota, 95-87. He also had 24 points, 23 rebounds and 1 assist.

Chris Kaman - Blocks

Chris Kaman blocks a career high 9 shots (2008)

On January 19, 2008, Chris Kaman set his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 9 blocks in LA Clippers's home win against New Jersey, 120-107. He also had 10 points, 12 rebounds and 1 assist.
